WEBVTT

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:38.040
Hurry.

00:01:38.359 --> 00:01:39.359
By secret order of the Empress Dowager,

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:41.920
go to All-Knowing Manor to track down the murderer.

00:01:42.480 --> 00:01:43.280
Go.

00:01:43.879 --> 00:01:45.959
Give them the Poison-Warding Pills.

00:01:46.319 --> 00:01:47.079
Yes.

00:02:03.719 --> 00:02:05.079
I'm here. Where are you?

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:09.159
How is it?

00:02:09.159 --> 00:02:10.120
Did you get the item?

00:02:12.719 --> 00:02:14.080
The killer couldn't silently

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:15.560
move the body immediately.

00:02:15.919 --> 00:02:17.599
So they hid the body here first.

00:02:18.639 --> 00:02:20.280
This path is behind the kitchen.

00:02:20.599 --> 00:02:21.919
Except for servants and laborers,

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:24.479
guests going to the main hall would never pass by here.

00:02:26.120 --> 00:02:27.319
At night when everyone was asleep,

00:02:27.479 --> 00:02:28.240
heaven helped,

00:02:28.240 --> 00:02:29.159
and it started raining again.

00:02:30.240 --> 00:02:32.800
The rain could not only mask the sound of moving the body,

00:02:33.360 --> 00:02:35.199
but also wash away the evidence.

00:02:39.280 --> 00:02:41.240
However, it was precisely because of this rain

00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:43.680
that a trail of rut marks was left on the road.

00:02:45.400 --> 00:02:46.719
And the bloody characters on the wall

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:48.479
were not written with Sixth Lord's blood,

00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:51.280
but with blood drained from killing a chicken here.

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:52.840
That's right.

00:02:54.240 --> 00:02:55.599
Writing with chicken blood...

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:58.479
if discovered, all efforts would be wasted.

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:02.800
So, the killer set fire to the room

00:03:03.159 --> 00:03:04.360
to destroy the evidence.

00:03:05.879 --> 00:03:08.360
So, who exactly is the killer?

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:09.199
Brother A-Liang,

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:10.360
be patient.

00:03:10.919 --> 00:03:11.879
The killer

00:03:19.360 --> 00:03:20.800
will appear very soon.

00:03:36.759 --> 00:03:37.560
Look at this.

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:44.439
This handwriting...

00:03:44.719 --> 00:03:45.840
Dali Temple has a copy

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:48.039
of a letter Huang Cui wrote personally to the Lord back then.

00:03:49.039 --> 00:03:50.599
This is a piece cut from it.

00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:54.319
Although the handwriting is slightly different,

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:57.400
from the brush strokes and writing habits,

00:03:58.360 --> 00:03:59.400
one can still see

00:03:59.639 --> 00:04:01.360
that it matches the bloody characters in Sixth Lord's room.

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:02.639
They came from the same hand.

00:04:03.639 --> 00:04:04.319
As expected,

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:06.199
Huang Cui is still in the manor.

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:07.319
Correct.

00:04:08.360 --> 00:04:10.599
And she is among Xiao Bai, Fourth Lady,

00:04:10.599 --> 00:04:12.159
and the Young Master.

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:15.879
You still suspect Fourth Lady?

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:18.439
I suspect them all.

00:04:19.000 --> 00:04:20.199
But her suspicion is the greatest.

00:04:21.360 --> 00:04:25.120
But would Fourth Lady need to, in her own room,

00:04:27.279 --> 00:04:29.240
fake a locked-room murder?

00:04:32.399 --> 00:04:33.079
It's hot.

00:04:33.480 --> 00:04:34.480
Be careful.

00:04:38.360 --> 00:04:39.519
Don't stack them together.

00:04:39.519 --> 00:04:40.399
Spread them out.

00:04:50.040 --> 00:04:50.800
Master Kun,

00:04:50.959 --> 00:04:51.879
do you know about water torture?

00:04:54.480 --> 00:04:55.600
You mean...

00:04:58.680 --> 00:04:59.439
the Paper Mask?

00:05:01.560 --> 00:05:03.959
It seems we have to go to Fourth Lady's place again.

00:05:11.120 --> 00:05:12.319
When we came this morning,

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:14.040
there was moisture on the table legs.

00:05:15.240 --> 00:05:18.040
It means the things burned contained moisture.

00:05:22.439 --> 00:05:22.920
Master Kun.

00:05:23.480 --> 00:05:23.879
You...

00:05:24.279 --> 00:05:24.959
What are you doing?

00:05:26.480 --> 00:05:27.079
Just cooperate a bit.

00:05:30.839 --> 00:05:33.839
If the killer took advantage of Ding Da being fast asleep,

00:05:34.480 --> 00:05:35.279
took a sheet of paper,

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:38.079
and covered his face with it...

00:05:40.399 --> 00:05:41.240
Master Kun,

00:05:41.279 --> 00:05:42.079
hold your breath.

00:05:46.279 --> 00:05:48.319
Then poured water

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:53.600
little by little onto the paper.

00:05:58.040 --> 00:05:59.600
Cover with a sheet of paper,

00:06:00.360 --> 00:06:01.680
pour water once.

00:06:03.720 --> 00:06:05.319
Cover with another sheet,

00:06:06.360 --> 00:06:08.800
pour water again.

00:06:23.680 --> 00:06:24.240
Look.

00:06:28.079 --> 00:06:29.120
This is why

00:06:30.439 --> 00:06:32.720
there was no weapon, but there was water vapor.

00:06:41.759 --> 00:06:42.639
Now,

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:45.759
as long as we figure out how this locked room was created,

00:06:46.199 --> 00:06:47.600
and how the killer got in and out,

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:49.800
this case will be solved.

00:06:55.360 --> 00:06:57.879
The sky is quite beautiful.

00:07:00.680 --> 00:07:03.600
Yellow clouds turning waves in the nine heavens.

00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:08.120
Isn't that right now?

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.279
You mean...

00:07:11.920 --> 00:07:13.120
"Yellow clouds" refers to dusk?

00:07:18.319 --> 00:07:19.839
Are you two watching the sunset?

00:07:21.800 --> 00:07:23.120
If you really want to see the sunset,

00:07:23.399 --> 00:07:25.839
there is a better place in the Manor than here.

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:28.240
Then may I ask, Miss Xiaobai,

00:07:28.639 --> 00:07:30.680
where is the best spot to view the sunset

00:07:30.680 --> 00:07:31.319
in the Manor?

00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:32.759
Could you take us to see it?

00:07:35.600 --> 00:07:36.279
Follow me.

00:07:46.480 --> 00:07:48.199
The Manor is divided in two by the Chi River.

00:07:48.759 --> 00:07:50.079
We are on the north bank,

00:07:50.079 --> 00:07:52.079
which is further divided into the East and West Courtyards.

00:07:52.360 --> 00:07:53.920
The Wanxiang Pavilion in the West Courtyard

00:07:53.920 --> 00:07:54.680
is the only place in the Manor

00:07:54.680 --> 00:07:56.920
where you can see the last glimpse of the sunset.

00:08:08.399 --> 00:08:09.240
Here we are.

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:12.160
Isn't this Wanxiang Pavilion?

00:08:21.600 --> 00:08:23.800
Has anyone else gone upstairs to watch the sunset?

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:26.079
To be honest, Miracle Doctor Du,

00:08:26.439 --> 00:08:28.240
the treasures on the first floor of Wanxiang Pavilion

00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:29.319
are all common items.

00:08:29.399 --> 00:08:31.920
The treasure on the second floor is this very scenery of "yellow clouds".

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:35.000
So the Manor's distinguished guests have all been invited by the Master

00:08:35.559 --> 00:08:36.799
to come up here and watch the clouds.

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:38.240
So,

00:08:39.240 --> 00:08:40.840
everyone else has figured out the first line of the poem?

00:08:41.759 --> 00:08:42.720
They all figured it out.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:46.440
It seems only you two, master and disciple,

00:08:46.559 --> 00:08:48.360
are not interested in cracking the code.

00:08:51.799 --> 00:08:54.360
However, everyone only guessed the first line.

00:08:55.039 --> 00:08:57.120
They are still clueless about the rest.

00:08:58.919 --> 00:08:59.840
The Miracle Doctor is brilliant.

00:09:00.159 --> 00:09:01.440
You will surely be the first to figure it out.

00:09:02.039 --> 00:09:02.840
This way, please.

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:08.919
When did you two get so close?

00:09:20.200 --> 00:09:21.000
Look.

00:09:21.360 --> 00:09:22.399
Looking out from here,

00:09:22.759 --> 00:09:24.480
you can see the sunset perfectly.

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:25.919
It's truly beautiful.

00:09:26.279 --> 00:09:28.320
This is the best spot in the Manor to watch the sunset.

00:09:34.840 --> 00:09:35.960
Viewing heaven and earth,

00:09:36.799 --> 00:09:38.759
holding hands to pluck the sun and moon.

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:44.679
Admiring flower shadows, a square inch holds the mortal world.

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:47.679
That's quite a boast.

00:09:49.360 --> 00:09:51.559
The Master gave this to his wife back then.

00:09:52.159 --> 00:09:54.120
This couplet is how they pledged their love.

00:09:55.039 --> 00:09:56.799
The Master hoped to accompany his wife,

00:09:57.120 --> 00:09:58.039
to watch heaven and earth,

00:09:58.159 --> 00:09:59.039
admire the beautiful scenery,

00:09:59.759 --> 00:10:00.879
and spend their whole lives like that.

00:10:02.279 --> 00:10:05.200
But I didn't expect it to be so dilapidated now.

00:10:07.240 --> 00:10:08.559
He is a sentimental man.

00:10:12.840 --> 00:10:13.720
Flower shadows.

00:10:16.159 --> 00:10:17.279
Water Immortal.

00:10:18.240 --> 00:10:20.240
Heaven calls forth the Water Immortal.

00:10:20.960 --> 00:10:22.720
Are there "Water Immortals" in this Manor?

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:25.440
There are no "Water Immortals".

00:10:26.200 --> 00:10:27.240
But there are lotuses.

00:10:29.399 --> 00:10:30.039
Over there.

00:10:37.879 --> 00:10:39.240
This is the Lotus Garden.

00:10:41.679 --> 00:10:43.080
The Madam loved lotuses.

00:10:43.519 --> 00:10:44.879
During summer dusks,

00:10:45.159 --> 00:10:46.440
standing upstairs in Wanxiang Pavilion,

00:10:46.919 --> 00:10:48.360
one could perfectly admire

00:10:48.360 --> 00:10:49.919
the beautiful scenery of the sunset shining on the Lotus Garden.

00:10:50.519 --> 00:10:52.600
So "Heaven calls forth the Water Immortal"

00:10:53.519 --> 00:10:54.440
refers to the Lotus Garden.

00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:56.360
These lotuses

00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:58.679
are the "flower shadows" in the couplet.

00:11:00.080 --> 00:11:02.360
Then why is the lotus pond gone?

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:06.639
After the Madam passed away,

00:11:06.639 --> 00:11:08.159
the Master was grief-stricken.

00:11:08.159 --> 00:11:09.440
He didn't want to be reminded of her by these things,

00:11:09.639 --> 00:11:10.840
so this place was abandoned.

00:11:11.519 --> 00:11:13.159
Only these four plants in the vat were kept.

00:11:13.559 --> 00:11:14.759
Made by the Master himself.

00:11:15.440 --> 00:11:16.799
If he didn't want to be reminded of her,

00:11:17.120 --> 00:11:18.039
he could just not come here.

00:11:18.279 --> 00:11:19.240
A man who loves his wife,

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:20.919
how could he let her favorite Lotus Garden go to ruin?

00:11:29.519 --> 00:11:30.320
Apart from these,

00:11:31.159 --> 00:11:32.000
there is nothing else.

00:11:34.679 --> 00:11:35.360
Perhaps

00:11:35.840 --> 00:11:39.840
the meaning of "Immortal points the way to the Book of Longevity"

00:11:40.639 --> 00:11:41.519
lies within this garden.

00:12:04.679 --> 00:12:05.879
My respects, Gonggong.

00:12:07.279 --> 00:12:08.639
The secret message...

00:12:08.919 --> 00:12:10.679
How far have you decoded it?

00:12:11.279 --> 00:12:12.080
I am dull-witted.

00:12:12.120 --> 00:12:13.279
I have only decoded the first two lines.

00:12:14.919 --> 00:12:16.120
What about the others?

00:12:17.799 --> 00:12:18.960
And Ye Li?

00:12:20.759 --> 00:12:22.320
Due to the sudden murders at the Manor,

00:12:22.799 --> 00:12:23.840
everyone has been distracted.

00:12:24.120 --> 00:12:25.120
We have only decoded up to this line.

00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:26.960
However, I...

00:12:27.159 --> 00:12:28.159
...have already destroyed the All-Knowing Manor's...

00:12:28.159 --> 00:12:29.360
...entire supply of Poison-Warding Pills.

00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:32.720
Now only we can come and go freely.

00:12:38.120 --> 00:12:40.600
Do you intend to go there personally, Gonggong?

00:12:41.879 --> 00:12:43.320
To make a trip...

00:12:43.639 --> 00:12:44.799
...would do no harm.

00:12:46.519 --> 00:12:49.480
If I do not see him beheaded with my own eyes,

00:12:50.679 --> 00:12:55.039
then the Jingzhao Yin died in vain.

00:13:04.240 --> 00:13:04.840
We're here.

00:13:05.240 --> 00:13:06.759
Let's go check the roof of Si Niang's room.

00:13:14.759 --> 00:13:15.480
Come on up.

00:13:16.360 --> 00:13:17.080
Master Kun.

00:13:17.279 --> 00:13:18.360
How am I supposed to get up there?

00:13:18.559 --> 00:13:19.840
I don't know martial arts!

00:13:21.399 --> 00:13:22.120
How about...

00:13:22.799 --> 00:13:24.080
...since you are my good apprentice...

00:13:24.080 --> 00:13:24.840
...you come down and carry me up?

00:13:33.240 --> 00:13:34.840
Master Kun, I'm afraid of heights!

00:13:38.960 --> 00:13:40.519
I say, can't you tread a little lighter?

00:13:44.679 --> 00:13:46.000
Look there. Someone moved the tiles.

00:13:55.919 --> 00:13:56.879
It must be right here.

00:14:04.320 --> 00:14:05.639
You mean to say...

00:14:06.840 --> 00:14:09.320
...the killer struck from the roof...

00:14:09.600 --> 00:14:10.879
...to murder Ding Da?